overview.en: CEBC is committed to developing a block chain ecosystem that combines block chain 3.0 technology with online shopping. CEBC team has a dual background of Internet e-commerce and financial science and technology. After deep understanding and detailed investigation of e-commerce development, CEBC team is determined to use block chain technology to solve the pain points.
overview.zh: CEBC 致力于开发一套将区块链 3.0 技术与线上购物相结合的区块链生态系统。CEBC 团队拥有互联网电商及金融科技双重背景，在对电商发展具备深刻认识和详细调研之后，决意采用区块链技术解决其中的痛点
